[Adapted from Jinjiang Wenxuecheng's
"Queen Liu Heipang", written by Ge Yang]

21
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:39,470
[The Legendary Life of Queen Lau]

22
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:40,403
[Episode 12]

23
00:01:40,403 --> 00:01:42,350
[This work is fictitious.
Any resemblance to reality is coincidental]

24
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:47,680
-I...
-Liu Baiyu.

25
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,239
You can just sit here.

26
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:52,040
But why? This isn't my seat.

27
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,800
Is your name on any other seats then?

28
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,080
You're not obeying the rules.

29
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,239
What rules?

30
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:57,040
If so, you...

31
00:01:57,839 --> 00:01:59,480
Don't interrupt Yunzhang when he's studying.

32
00:02:20,199 --> 00:02:21,199
(What's going on?)

33
00:02:21,559 --> 00:02:22,960
(Is he not in his right mind?)

34
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:25,080
(Why is he smiling at me instead of Liu Baiyu?)

35
00:02:29,679 --> 00:02:30,440
All right.

36
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:35,960
Today, we'll learn about rhythm.

37
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:44,660
[Diligent and Committed]

38
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,720
(Later, I'll give Baiyu a serious beating)

39
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,119
(and call her a wretch.)

40
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,119
(I'll make His Majesty hate me,)

41
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,279
(despise me,)

42
00:03:27,279 --> 00:03:29,199
(and make him think that I'm cruel and ruthless.)

43
00:03:29,559 --> 00:03:32,440
(That way, I can return to Xianpa Village.)

44
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,559
(Seems like I can only use music)

45
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,320
(to quell Jinfeng's rage)

46
00:03:46,839 --> 00:03:47,960
(and grudge.)

47
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,960
His Majesty will take this path every day
in order to get to the academy.

48
00:03:57,880 --> 00:04:00,320
Why don't we forget about it today?

49
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:02,119
Do you think His Majesty will believe us?

50
00:04:02,839 --> 00:04:04,679
If you can't reach the man,
you should at least stop him in his track.

51
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,479
Later, when His Majesty is here,
just pretend to bump into him.

52
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,600
After that, tell him

53
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:09,320
that I maligned you for stealing the brush.

54
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,279
Understood?

55
00:04:11,119 --> 00:04:12,520
He will surely be suspicious.

56
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,119
Be suspicious?

57
00:04:13,119 --> 00:04:14,679
If so, you can just convince him.

58
00:04:14,679 --> 00:04:15,639
-I...
-You're so dumb.

59
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,279
He's coming!

60
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,200
Are you ready?

61
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:18,959
Go!

62
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,279
(This time, I'll show you how vicious I am.)

63
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,440
(Go ahead and criticize me.)

64
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:27,940
[Study and Teach with Enthusiasm]

65
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,239
Your Majesty!

66
00:04:29,239 --> 00:04:30,799
Your Majesty, you must uphold justice for me!

67
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,959
I lost the hare fur brush

68
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,679
that Her Majesty
was going to present to Your Majesty.

69
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,679
Her Majesty is going to inflict
cruel punishment on me!

70
00:04:37,239 --> 00:04:37,880
What?

71
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:39,559
Miss Baiyu, you're such a jokester.

72
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:42,239
Although Sister-in-law does like
to mess around with the maidservants,

73
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:44,079
she has never hurt nor reprimanded
the maidservants.

74
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:46,079
She's going to inflict cruel punishment on you

75
00:04:46,239 --> 00:04:47,679
just because you lost her hare fur brush?

76
00:04:48,119 --> 00:04:49,320
Do you think Yunzhang

77
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,440
will believe in your words?

78
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,079
You don't even know how to lie.

79
00:04:52,239 --> 00:04:53,239
What a joke.

80
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:55,640
Miss Baiyu, I think you misunderstood Jinfeng.

81
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,440
I think she was just joking around.

82
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,839
Your Majesty, don't listen to her nonsense!

83
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,679
You wretch!

84
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,200
Your Majesty,

85
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,320
please listen to me.

86
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,279
I found a pair

87
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:07,519
of excellent hare fur brushes.

88
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,880
Initially, I wanted to present you
with one of them.

89
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:11,320
I didn't expect this wretch to lose it!

90
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:12,559
You did it on purpose!

91
00:05:15,679 --> 00:05:17,959
(Jinfeng is becoming jealous
and her personality has changed.)

92
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:20,600
(Seems like she's deeply in love with me.)

93
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,000
(It's my fault.)

94
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:25,720
(Everything is my fault.)

95
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,160
Wait!

96
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:30,880
Your Majesty, I...

97
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,440
You wretch! How dare you still speak?

98
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:33,959
Jinfeng, you did the right thing.

99
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,600
Actually, it doesn't matter

100
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,799
if I receive the gift or not.

101
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,920
However, Liu Baiyu actually lost the gift

102
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:43,279
which you had prepared especially for me.

103
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,799
She had made you upset too.

104
00:05:46,559 --> 00:05:47,239
She deserved to be punished.

105
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,239
What?

106
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,920
I said, Jinfeng, you did the right thing.

107
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,799
It was an excellent punishment.

108
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,000
Wait, you...

109
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,839
I'm going to inflict cruel punishment on her soon.

110
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:58,920
But I believe His Majesty has his boundaries.

111
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,000
I'm sure he won't allow his queen

112
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,000
to be this cruel, right?

113
00:06:01,679 --> 00:06:02,799
Jinfeng, you said so yourself.

114
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,920
It's all because

115
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,200
you're too deeply in love with me.

116
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:07,679
There's no fault in love.

117
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:09,399
How do you plan to punish her?

118
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,239
Why don't we make her
copy The Analects of Confucius?

119
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,200
If so, we shall follow Jinfeng's will.

120
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,920
You are to return to the Imperial Academy
and copy The Analects of Confucius

121
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,000
a hundred times.

122
00:06:21,239 --> 00:06:22,559
No mistakes or omissions are allowed.

123
00:06:22,559 --> 00:06:23,959
You are not to skive.

124
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:24,640
If not,

125
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:28,920
What do you think about this arrangement?

126
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,079
It's pretty good.

127
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,640
If there's nothing else, I shall leave for now.

128
00:06:35,820 --> 00:06:35,860
I'll let Jinfeng handle your punishment.

129
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:41,180
[Study and Teach with Enthusiasm]

130
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,000
Cut the act. Get up.

131
00:06:43,799 --> 00:06:45,600
Our act was pretty convincing just now.

132
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,720
Why did it fail?

133
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:47,920
I...

134
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:50,160
Is this the plan you had mentioned?

135
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,200
Baiyu?

136
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:54,839
Baiyu, are you angry at me?

137
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,839
I'll join you for the punishment.

138
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,399
Hey.

139
00:07:04,839 --> 00:07:05,600
Tell me,

140
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:08,279
what do you guys think about
Jinfeng's behavior today?

141
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,200
Your Majesty,

142
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,359
I was shocked

143
00:07:11,359 --> 00:07:12,720
when Her Majesty gave her a slap.

144
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,519
I wonder what's wrong with Her Majesty lately?

145
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,239
It's as if she had a change of heart.

146
00:07:17,239 --> 00:07:18,000
Tang, what about you?

147
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,760
In my opinion,

148
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,399
I think Your Majesty is acting strange.

149
00:07:21,799 --> 00:07:23,399
It's fine that you aren't punishing Her Majesty.

150
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,920
However, you actually pampered her

151
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,799
and backed her up.

152
00:07:26,119 --> 00:07:28,399
I think Your Majesty went too far.

153
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,679
Yunchong,

154
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,200
tell them about it.

155
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:36,040
What you guys saw was merely a false front.

156
00:07:36,119 --> 00:07:37,519
This is one of Yunzhang's plans.

157
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,399
He did it so that the brewing storm

158
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:40,600
could be quelled.

159
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,839
At least, we went through the day

160
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,760
without any mishaps, right?

161
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,519
Wait, you do have a point.

162
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:49,880
When Her Majesty slapped Liu Baiyu,

163
00:07:50,239 --> 00:07:51,679
it was as if she was trying to tear her apart.

164
00:07:52,359 --> 00:07:54,160
But it ended up with Liu Baiyu
copying The Analects of Confucius.

165
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,040
Your Majesty is wise indeed.

166
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,600
I can truly have peace of mind now.

167
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,679
Yunzhang always showed great foresight.

168
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,119
He was always impressive to me.

169
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:03,679
However,

170
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,359
I'm a little worried about tomorrow.

171
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,519
What's wrong with tomorrow?

172
00:08:07,799 --> 00:08:08,880
Didn't Grand Tutor Wei

173
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,320
say this when our class was over?

174
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:13,119
Currently, this is the best time
for people to go on an outing.

175
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:15,239
To enjoy the breeze on the hill
and to sing on the way home.

176
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,279
Even Confucius is in favor of this idea.

177
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,920
Members of the imperial family like us

178
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,519
should follow the ancient customs

179
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:22,000
and abide by the law of nature.

180
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,519
That's why we should make a secret trip
and enjoy the occasion together with the people.

181
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,720
It's just a trip.

182
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,040
What's there to be nervous about?

183
00:08:28,239 --> 00:08:29,279
Yunzhang, think about it.

184
00:08:29,559 --> 00:08:31,040
Liu Baiyu is already on bad terms
with Her Majesty

185
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,640
in the palace.

186
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,880
Without restraints,
I'm sure all hell will break loose

187
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,159
when we leave the palace.

188
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,239
If they do fight each other,

189
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,719
they'll turn into laughing stocks
for the people to see.

190
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,039
You're right.

191
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,159
I was careless.

192
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:48,679
Maybe both of them are trying to come up with ways

193
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,000
to attract my attention tomorrow.

194
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,520
Your Majesty,

195
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,640
Tie and I will surely stay by your side

196
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:54,599
and protect you tomorrow.

197
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,359
No need for that.

198
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,719
You guys can stay out of this.

199
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,280
But Yunchong,

200
00:08:59,599 --> 00:09:00,679
from tomorrow onward,

201
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,880
you need to monitor Baiyu closely.

202
00:09:03,599 --> 00:09:04,359
And I

203
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,679
will monitor Jinfeng closely.

204
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,239
Yes, Your Majesty.

205
00:09:19,119 --> 00:09:19,840
[Study and Teach with Enthusiasm]
Your Majesty,

206
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,520
[Study Hard and Uphold Justice]
stop sighing.

207
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,400
Liu Baiyu was angry at you

208
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,000
for no reason.

209
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,679
You did everything for her sake.

210
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:31,080
However, I did fail to act

211
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,559
like a jealous and evil queen.

212
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:33,599
Say, why can't Duan Yunzhang

213
00:09:33,599 --> 00:09:35,039
just play by the rules?

214
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:35,719
Your Majesty,

215
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:38,599
why don't we look at it from another perspective?

216
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,960
We should ask Liu Baiyu
to put in more effort herself.

217
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:44,960
What is that?

218
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:47,119
The Search For Love.

219
00:09:47,479 --> 00:09:48,479
This is the newest book

220
00:09:48,479 --> 00:09:50,239
written by Lovely Breeze and Bright Moonlight.

221
00:09:50,239 --> 00:09:52,039
It's known as the new bible of love.

222
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:54,400
It's widely popular among
the maidservants nowadays.

223
00:09:55,479 --> 00:09:57,239
Not bad at all, Sufang.

224
00:09:57,239 --> 00:09:59,080
Why didn't you show it to me earlier?

225
00:09:59,719 --> 00:10:02,280
Your Majesty, it's because I can only read it

226
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,840
after your class is over.

227
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,039
When there's a will, there's a way.

228
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:11,119
Coincidentally, Grand Tutor Wei
will bring us out of the palace tomorrow.

229
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,400
I guess we can use this.

230
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,000
Baiyu, are you not done yet?

231
00:10:38,479 --> 00:10:39,520
I'm sure you're almost done, right?

232
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:40,760
That's right.

233
00:10:41,359 --> 00:10:42,479
I'm glad to hear that.

234
