00:27:14,540 --> 00:27:15,420
Take your turns.

723
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:18,580
You can take over.

724
00:27:18,740 --> 00:27:19,580
I'll help them out.

725
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:20,340
Go ahead.

726
00:27:26,300 --> 00:27:26,860
Go now.

727
00:27:41,180 --> 00:27:41,780
Your Majesty,

728
00:27:41,940 --> 00:27:43,580
although you don't know much about me,

729
00:27:43,580 --> 00:27:45,620
I've heard about your story since I was little.

730
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:50,780
Since you were little, Your Majesty
had shown impressive intellect.

731
00:27:50,780 --> 00:27:53,020
Not only were you elegant, educated,
and ambitious,

732
00:27:53,020 --> 00:27:55,420
but you were also a virtuous ruler.

733
00:27:55,540 --> 00:27:56,620
It's a shame

734
00:27:56,620 --> 00:27:58,340
that there was no one

735
00:27:58,620 --> 00:28:00,420
to keep you company

736
00:28:00,420 --> 00:28:01,900
and share your burdens with you.

737
00:28:02,500 --> 00:28:03,100
Your Majesty,

738
00:28:03,500 --> 00:28:05,140
I'm sure you were lonely.

739
00:28:05,620 --> 00:28:06,620
(Great job.)

740
00:28:07,060 --> 00:28:08,580
(Third step in courting your love,)

741
00:28:08,780 --> 00:28:11,220
(penetrate the superficial skin
and reach deep into the soul.)

742
00:28:11,300 --> 00:28:13,420
(To show your support as a gentle lady.)

743
00:28:13,420 --> 00:28:14,060
Is that so?

744
00:28:14,940 --> 00:28:16,340
So, are you saying

745
00:28:16,340 --> 00:28:18,140
that not even my mother

746
00:28:18,140 --> 00:28:19,220
or any one of my trusted aides

747
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:22,060
can understand what I'm thinking?

748
00:28:22,060 --> 00:28:22,740
Are you saying

749
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:25,580
that I've been living in misery all these years?

750
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,220
No!

751
00:28:28,420 --> 00:28:30,620
That's not what I mean!

752
00:28:30,620 --> 00:28:31,420
That's not it.

753
00:28:31,420 --> 00:28:32,380
That's it.

754
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:34,300
That's not what I mean.

755
00:28:38,580 --> 00:28:39,420
Let's dig in for now.

756
00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:43,060
I...

757
00:29:00,060 --> 00:29:01,660
It's so spicy.

758
00:29:05,740 --> 00:29:06,540
(Now,)

759
00:29:06,540 --> 00:29:07,980
(you guys have a common topic.)

760
00:29:08,140 --> 00:29:10,140
(I'll scare you out of your mind today)

761
00:29:10,140 --> 00:29:12,420
(so that you can recognize who your true love is.)

762
00:29:13,020 --> 00:29:14,180
The ribs are pretty good.

763
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:21,300
So delicious.

764
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:22,700
(So, it's not enough.)

765
00:29:22,700 --> 00:29:24,700
(Seems like I need to do something extra.)

766
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:25,420
Your Majesty.

767
00:29:26,060 --> 00:29:27,180
What are you doing?

768
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:28,340
You should forget about the formalities

769
00:29:28,340 --> 00:29:29,900
now that you're out of the palace.

770
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:30,700
Throw away your chopsticks!

771
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:31,700
Use your hands!

772
00:29:32,300 --> 00:29:34,180
I like to use chopsticks.
What can you do about it?

773
00:29:34,180 --> 00:29:34,660
Your Majesty,

774
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:35,700
I know you the best.

775
00:29:35,700 --> 00:29:36,580
Stop pretending to be stubborn.

776
00:29:36,580 --> 00:29:37,620
Your inner beast

777
00:29:37,620 --> 00:29:39,340
was always chained down
by those obnoxious palace rules.

778
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:40,900
Here, let me unshackle you.

779
00:29:41,980 --> 00:29:44,060
(Seems like she's trying to trick me again.)

780
00:29:44,860 --> 00:29:46,460
(Could this be one of their plots too?)

781
00:29:49,020 --> 00:29:50,180
Your Majesty, what are you doing?

782
00:29:50,660 --> 00:29:52,740
I suddenly think that Jinfeng has a point.

783
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:54,020
Miss Baiyu, you should join us too.

784
00:29:54,020 --> 00:29:55,020
Throw away your chopsticks.

785
00:29:55,020 --> 00:29:55,860
No, Your Majesty.

786
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:57,780
I don't think this is appropriate.

787
00:29:58,060 --> 00:30:00,300
Your Majesty, you should lead by example.

788
00:30:00,540 --> 00:30:02,300
Miss Baiyu knows the people better than me.

789
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:03,060
Baiyu shall do it first.

790
00:30:03,060 --> 00:30:05,020
I have no choice but to defy you, Your Majesty!

791
00:30:05,020 --> 00:30:06,220
Just kill me already!

792
00:30:06,380 --> 00:30:07,700
Your Majesty, go ahead!

793
00:30:07,980 --> 00:30:09,180
It's either we both throw away our chopsticks

794
00:30:09,180 --> 00:30:11,260
or you let go of me right now.

795
00:30:12,900 --> 00:30:13,500
Your Majesty!

796
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:16,340
What are you guys doing?

797
00:30:19,700 --> 00:30:20,700
It's lucky that I came up

798
00:30:20,700 --> 00:30:21,700
with that excellent move.

799
00:30:21,700 --> 00:30:22,500
If not,

800
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:23,860
Liu Baiyu would laugh at me

801
00:30:23,860 --> 00:30:24,940
if she knew that I was tailing her.

802
00:30:25,300 --> 00:30:26,020
Now,

803
00:30:26,020 --> 00:30:27,140
I'll pretend that it was a coincidence.

804
00:30:27,820 --> 00:30:28,580
A coincidence.

805
00:30:29,460 --> 00:30:30,140
Get out of the way!

806
00:30:30,380 --> 00:30:31,020
What are you guys doing?

807
00:30:32,420 --> 00:30:33,180
Who are you guys?

808
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:34,540
I carved Miss Baiyu's name

809
00:30:34,540 --> 00:30:35,460
on my arm

810
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:36,500
and I kiss it every day.

811
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:37,780
You should kiss the real deal.

812
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:38,740
I would die for it.

813
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:39,700
Such wishful thinking!

814
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:41,780
You have to bring her to a quiet place

815
00:30:41,780 --> 00:30:43,260
before you do anything to her.

816
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:44,820
Listen,

817
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:45,700
I just want

818
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:46,580
a handkerchief with her sweat on it.

819
00:30:46,580 --> 00:30:47,980
So, they're Liu Baiyu's admirers.

820
00:30:48,140 --> 00:30:49,300
No wonder they're so rude.

821
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:53,380
Kiss her? Her handkerchief?

822
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:54,820
Do anything to her?

823
00:30:56,020 --> 00:30:57,140
They disgust me.

824
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:01,580
So, you guys are here?

825
00:31:05,860 --> 00:31:07,140
-Your Majesty!
-What are you guys doing?

826
00:31:12,140 --> 00:31:13,060
Is this a three-way tug-of-war?

827
00:31:15,660 --> 00:31:16,500
Just put it down.

828
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:17,260
There are other people here.

829
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:18,540
-She should let go!
-He should let go!

830
00:31:19,940 --> 00:31:21,420
All of you are members of the imperial palace.

831
00:31:21,820 --> 00:31:23,100
Do you guys need to resort to this

832
00:31:23,100 --> 00:31:23,900
for a pair of chopsticks?

833
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:25,660
Let go of me.

834
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:28,060
-No way!
-Let go of me!

835
00:31:28,740 --> 00:31:29,700
These should be enough for you.

836
00:31:30,260 --> 00:31:32,140
Come.

837
00:31:32,420 --> 00:31:33,900
It's been a while.

838
00:31:34,860 --> 00:31:35,540
Everyone,

839
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:36,740
following the usual,

840
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:38,660
each of us shall recite one verse

841
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:41,300
to praise our goddess, Miss Baiyu.

842
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:42,220
What do you guys think?

843
00:31:42,300 --> 00:31:43,340
Great!

844
00:31:43,940 --> 00:31:44,780
Baiyu,

845
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:47,060
did someone mention your name just now?

846
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:49,380
Who are they? They're so noisy.

847
00:31:51,020 --> 00:31:53,020
It's nothing. They are just my admirers.

848
00:31:53,820 --> 00:31:55,980
Your admirers?

849
00:31:56,340 --> 00:31:58,340
I'm not deaf. I can hear what she said.

850
00:31:58,340 --> 00:31:59,140
I shall go ahead then.

851
00:31:59,780 --> 00:32:02,460
Born with beauty, her eyebrows glow.

852
00:32:03,660 --> 00:32:04,860
What a great verse!

853
00:32:04,980 --> 00:32:06,740
What? You?

854
00:32:06,980 --> 00:32:08,300
Born with beauty?

855
00:32:08,780 --> 00:32:09,860
That's not true.

856
00:32:09,860 --> 00:32:11,060
I'll start the topic then.

857
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:12,100
Go ahead.

858
00:32:12,340 --> 00:32:13,140
I have one for her too.

859
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:14,380
Full of talents, her value grows.

860
00:32:14,380 --> 00:32:16,060
Full of talents?

861
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:17,700
What a great verse.

862
00:32:18,020 --> 00:32:19,260
No one would believe that.

863
00:32:19,500 --> 00:32:20,700
Let me think.

864
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:22,380
Don't restrain yourself.

865
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:24,140
My heart is aching

866
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:26,540
as I long for her!

867
00:32:27,900 --> 00:32:29,700
My goodness, his heart is aching.

868
00:32:31,300 --> 00:32:32,540
He's an idiot.

869
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:33,980
I!

870
00:32:34,220 --> 00:32:35,220
Here, Sister-in-law.

871
00:32:35,220 --> 00:32:36,700
You're welcome. We're on the same side.

872
00:32:36,940 --> 00:32:37,740
It's my duty to help you out.

873
00:32:39,260 --> 00:32:41,060
Look. Isn't that Miss Baiyu?

874
00:32:41,140 --> 00:32:41,980
That's right.

875
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:43,820
Baiyu, they saw you.

876
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:45,700
That's right. Look.

877
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:46,620
She's right opposite us.

878
00:32:47,140 --> 00:32:47,700
It is Miss Baiyu.

879
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:48,300
Baiyu,

880
00:32:48,580 --> 00:32:49,620
follow me to their side.

881
00:32:49,620 --> 00:32:50,140
But why?

882
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:51,820
Time to show them your charm.

883
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:53,420
Let's go.

884
00:32:53,900 --> 00:32:55,820
Miss Baiyu!

885
00:32:56,660 --> 00:32:57,260
Miss Baiyu!

886
00:32:57,260 --> 00:32:58,940
Miss Baiyu, I was lucky enough
to encounter you once before this.

887
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:00,700
She does look like the person in the portrait.

888
00:33:00,780 --> 00:33:01,420
That's right!

889
00:33:01,860 --> 00:33:02,700
Miss Baiyu!

890
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:03,460
I know that!

891
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:04,340
I have admired you for a long time!

892
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:05,740
I've read every poem you've written!

893
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:06,660
-Me too!
-Me too!

894
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,340
Miss Baiyu!

895
00:33:07,340 --> 00:33:07,580
Thank you.

896
00:33:07,580 --> 00:33:08,620
I have a go manual
that was passed down from my family.

897
00:33:08,620 --> 00:33:09,700
I always wanted to study it

898
00:33:09,700 --> 00:33:10,700
together with you.

899
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:11,620
Me too!

900
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:13,980
Miss Baiyu!

901
00:33:13,980 --> 00:33:14,860
Your Majesty!

902
00:33:15,220 --> 00:33:16,060
It's fine.

903
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:17,660
They're your admirers.

904
00:33:17,660 --> 00:33:18,540
I don't think they'll do anything to you.

905
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:19,740
That's right.

906
00:33:19,740 --> 00:33:20,540
Miss Baiyu!

907
00:33:20,540 --> 00:33:21,540
Please sign here for me!

908
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:22,820
-Me too!
-Me too!

909
00:33:23,580 --> 00:33:24,420
-Don't touch her.
-Don't do this!

910
00:33:25,020 --> 00:33:26,340
Don't touch her!

911
00:33:26,340 --> 00:33:27,220
Wait!

912
00:33:27,460 --> 00:33:28,660
-Miss Baiyu!
-Stop dragging her!

913
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:30,340
Stop dragging her!

914
00:33:30,860 --> 00:33:31,940
-Stop!
-Who are you guys?

915
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:32,500
Let's go!

916
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:33,340
-Who are you?
-We'll make a move first!

917
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:34,300
Come on!

918
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:35,700
-Miss Baiyu!
-Miss Baiyu!

919
00:33:35,700 --> 00:33:36,060
Your Majesty!

920
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:37,500
-Miss Baiyu!
-Miss Baiyu!

921
00:33:37,500 --> 00:33:38,300
Wait for me!

922
00:33:49,580 --> 00:33:50,860
That's all the money you brought?

923
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:52,420
We're not here to indulge ourselves.

924
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:53,900
Why should I bring that much money with me?

925
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:55,340
What about you? I'm sure you brought a lot.

926
00:33:55,620 --> 00:33:57,020
I only brought a sack of gold taels.

927
00:33:57,020 --> 00:33:58,340
I already gave it to the flower seller.

928
00:34:00,220 --> 00:34:01,060
Sir and Madam,

929
00:34:01,700 --> 00:34:02,820
this isn't enough

930
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:05,460
to pay the bills for all three tables.

931
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:06,940
What about this?

932
00:34:07,820 --> 00:34:09,380
One of you can stay here

933
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,020
while the other can head back
and retrieve the money.

934
00:34:11,620 --> 00:34:12,500
Wait, sir.

935
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:13,500
I don't understand.

936
00:34:13,500 --> 00:34:14,620
Why must we pay

937
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:15,820
for the other two tables as well?

938
00:34:16,020 --> 00:34:18,340
They went after your friend.

939
00:34:18,340 --> 00:34:20,300
Of course, you have to pay for them.

940
00:34:20,460 --> 00:34:22,020
I didn't touch their food at all!

941
00:34:22,020 --> 00:34:24,100
Enough. Don't be so calculative.

942
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:25,100
It's just two tables.

943
00:34:25,660 --> 00:34:27,020
So, is the discount you mentioned still valid?

944
00:34:27,140 --> 00:34:27,860
Discount?

945
00:34:29,780 --> 00:34:31,180
So, you two are a couple?

946
00:34:32,860 --> 00:34:33,700
Wait.

947
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:35,420
They said they weren't a couple.

948
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:36,540
That's right. We're not a couple.

949
00:34:37,220 --> 00:34:37,700
Sir,

950
00:34:37,700 --> 00:34:38,460
can we work here

951
00:34:38,460 --> 00:34:39,380
to pay for the bills?

952
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:40,580
I can do the dishes for you.

953
00:34:41,220 --> 00:34:42,420
(This way, I don't need to return to the palace.)

954
00:34:42,420 --> 00:34:43,460
(I can even look for Mother.)

955
00:34:43,460 --> 00:34:44,740
(This is a blessing in disguise.)

956
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:45,980
What do you mean by that?

957
00:34:46,220 --> 00:34:47,420
You don't want to head back?

958
00:34:47,660 --> 00:34:49,140
That's not it. You misunderstood me.

959
00:34:49,220 --> 00:34:50,100
I was just thinking

960
00:34:50,100 --> 00:34:52,340
that we shouldn't owe people any money.

961
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,300
Sir, where's the kitchen?

962
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:55,140
I'll do the dishes right now.

963
00:34:55,220 --> 00:34:56,180
It's just the dishes, isn't it?

964
00:34:56,620 --> 00:34:57,380
I can do them too.

965
00:34:57,380 --> 00:34:58,020
No, you can't.

966
00:34:58,020 --> 00:34:59,900
You're not used to doing chores.
You won't be able to do them.

967
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,580
It's not like my hands will be ruined
if I do them.

968
00:35:01,740 --> 00:35:02,500
I can learn.

969
00:35:02,580 --> 00:35:04,460
I'm just afraid that we have
to pay more if you smash the dishes.

970
00:35:04,460 --> 00:35:06,380
If so, we can do the dishes
until we make enough to pay off the bill.

971
00:35:06,740 --> 00:35:07,500
What are you talking about?

972
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:09,540
Sir and Madam, please stop arguing.

973
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:10,740
Qingyun Restaurant

974
00:35:10,940 --> 00:35:11,980
doesn't accept labor work

975
00:35:11,980 --> 00:35:13,740
in exchange for the meal.

976
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:16,420
However, we do have another way

977
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,580
for you to make some money.

978
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:23,380
Ladies and gentlemen,

979
00:35:23,620 --> 00:35:26,700
welcome to our annual

980
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:29,100
flower-identifying contest!

981
00:35:29,620 --> 00:35:30,700
This contest

982
00:35:30,700 --> 00:35:32,780
