992
00:35:50,020 --> 00:35:50,820
The prize money

993
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:52,860
is enough for you to pay up
to 10 times your current bill.

994
00:35:53,420 --> 00:35:54,300
Sir and Madam, what do you think?

995
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:56,060
Don't just stand here. Just join it.

996
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:58,060
Since you two are a couple,

997
00:35:58,060 --> 00:35:59,460
I'm sure you two can outdo yourselves.

998
00:35:59,460 --> 00:36:00,980
