1000
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:05,660
One of you just had to go back
and retrieve the money.

1001
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:07,060
But you two insist on

1002
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:09,180
arguing with each other because of that.

1003
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:10,580
It's obvious that you two are a couple.

1004
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:12,180
It was a false front.

1005
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:15,500
I know the argument was a false front.

1006
00:36:16,580 --> 00:36:18,860
But that's the newest way
of showing off one's relationship.

1007
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:20,540
It's the latest trend. I know that.

1008
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:21,620
I know all about that.

1009
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:23,020
-We want to join the contest!
-We want to join the contest!

1010
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:24,700
Go now!

1011
00:36:24,700 --> 00:36:26,020
The contest will run out of slots soon!

1012
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:27,380
We have two contestants over here!

1013
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:28,140
Don't do that!

1014
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:29,100
Hurry!

1015
00:36:29,100 --> 00:36:30,180
Go now!

1016
00:36:30,500 --> 00:36:31,340
Just go already!

1017
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:35,500
Hurry!

1018
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:40,460
Miss Baiyu!

1019
00:36:40,460 --> 00:36:41,420
Look at me!

1020
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:42,380
Miss Baiyu!

1021
00:36:42,380 --> 00:36:44,300
-Miss Baiyu, give me your signature!
-Hurry!

1022
00:36:44,700 --> 00:36:45,580
Miss Baiyu!

1023
00:36:45,580 --> 00:36:47,700
Miss Baiyu! Don't run!

1024
00:36:48,180 --> 00:36:49,620
Miss Baiyu!

1025
00:36:49,820 --> 00:36:51,500
Why is Miss Baiyu

1026
00:36:52,180 --> 00:36:53,620
together with Prince Yunchong right now?

1027
00:36:53,620 --> 00:36:54,660
(Miss Baiyu!)

1028
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:56,900
The affairs of the imperial family
are confusing indeed.

1029
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:59,660
Now, I will announce the rules.

1030
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,000
Our rules are simple.

1031
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,399
The contestants shall take turns

1032
00:37:03,479 --> 00:37:06,080
to smell the scent of the flowers inside the box.

1033
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:06,919
After that,

1034
00:37:06,919 --> 00:37:09,879
the contestants need to identify
and tell us the types of flowers inside the box.

1035
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:11,159
One type of flower for each round.

1036
00:37:11,639 --> 00:37:13,000
Those who answered incorrectly
will be eliminated.

1037
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:15,239
The last man standing will be our winner.

1038
00:37:15,239 --> 00:37:17,159
Baiyu! Yunchong!

1039
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:19,159
Over there!

1040
00:37:19,159 --> 00:37:19,719
Hurry!

1041
