are too complicated.

1056
00:37:50,639 --> 00:37:51,919
Luckily, we didn't dine and dash.

1057
00:37:52,280 --> 00:37:53,679
My mother was right.

1058
00:37:53,679 --> 00:37:55,679
We can only live with peace of mind
if we retain our conscience.

1059
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:57,360
